# 太空射击游戏：星际保卫战

下面是一个完整的HTML5太空射击游戏，专为手机端优化设计，代码量约1200行。游戏包含多种敌人类型、能量收集、升级系统和关卡设计。

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>星际保卫战 - 太空射击游戏</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            touch-action: none;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial Rounded MT Bold', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c0e1d, #1a1f3d);
            color: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            perspective: 1000px;
        }

        .game-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            height: 100vh;
            max-height: 800px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            background: rgba(10, 15, 35, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 150, 255, 0.2);
        }

        canvas {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .ui-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .top-ui {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .score-container, .lives-container, .level-container {
            background: rgba(0, 20, 40, 0.7);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .score-title, .lives-title, .level-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64c8ff;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .score-value, .lives-value, .level-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.7);
        }

        .bottom-ui {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .powerup-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .powerup {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0, 30, 60, 0.7);
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.7);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .control-btn {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(0, 30, 60, 0.7);
            border: 2px solid rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.7);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #64c8ff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.5);
            pointer-events: auto;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .control-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
            background: rgba(0, 80, 150, 0.7);
        }

        .game-over {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
        }

        .game-over.active {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .game-over h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ff6464;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 100, 100, 0.7);
        }

        .final-score {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #64c8ff;
        }

        .restart-btn {
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc, #003366);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            pointer-events: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .restart-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .start-screen {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 90;
            opacity: 1;
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
        }

        .start-screen.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .start-screen h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #64c8ff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(100, 200, 255, 0.7);
        }

        .instructions {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        .instructions p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .start-btn {
            padding: 15px 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00cc66, #006633);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 200, 100, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .start-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .particles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .control-btn {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .powerup {
                width: 40px;
                height: 40px;
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .score-value, .lives-value, .level-value {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="game-container">
        <canvas id="gameCanvas"></canvas>
        <div class="particles" id="particles"></div>

        <div class="ui-container">
            <div class="top-ui">
                <div class="score-container">
                    <div class="score-title">分数</div>
                    <div class="score-value" id="score">0</div>
                </div>
                <div class="level-container">
                    <div class="level-title">关卡</div>
                    <div class="level-value" id="level">1</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lives-container">
                    <div class="lives-title">生命值</div>
                    <div class="lives-value" id="lives">3</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bottom-ui">
                <div class="powerup-container">
                    <div class="powerup" id="powerup1">✚</div>
                    <div class="powerup" id="powerup2">✚</div>
                    <div class="powerup" id="powerup3">✚</div>
                </div>
                <div class="controls">
                    <div class="control-btn" id="leftBtn">◀</div>
                    <div class="control-btn" id="fireBtn">●</div>
                    <div class="control-btn" id="rightBtn">▶</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="start-screen" id="startScreen">
            <h1>星际保卫战</h1>
            <div class="instructions">
                <p>🛸 左右滑动或点击按钮移动飞船</p>
                <p>💥 点击中间按钮发射子弹</p>
                <p>⭐ 收集能量提升武器威力</p>
                <p>💀 躲避敌人攻击，消灭所有敌人</p>
                <p>🌌 每关敌人数量和速度会增加</p>
            </div>
            <button class="start-btn" id="startBtn">开始游戏</button>
        </div>

        <div class="game-over" id="gameOver">
            <h1>游戏结束</h1>
            <div class="final-score">最终分数: <span id="finalScore">0</span></div>
            <button class="restart-btn" id="restartBtn">重新开始</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 游戏常量
        const CONFIG = {
            CANVAS_WIDTH: 500,
            CANVAS_HEIGHT: 800,
            PLAYER_SPEED: 8,
            BULLET_SPEED: 10,
            ENEMY_SPEED: 2,
            POWERUP_SPEED: 3,
            PLAYER_SIZE: 40,
            ENEMY_SIZE: 30,
            BULLET_SIZE: 8,
            POWERUP_SIZE: 25,
            MAX_ENEMIES: 8,
            MAX_BULLETS: 50,
            MAX_POWERUPS: 3,
            SPAWN_RATE: 60,
            POWERUP_SPAWN_RATE: 200,
            LEVEL_UP_THRESHOLD: 500,
            LEVEL_SPEED_INCREASE: 0.2,
            LEVEL_ENEMY_INCREASE: 1
        };

        // 游戏状态
        const gameState = {
            score: 0,
            lives: 3,
            level: 1,
            gameOver: false,
            gameStarted: false,
            keys: {},
            touchStartX: 0,
            playerX: CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH / 2,
            playerY: CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT - 100,
            bullets: [],
            enemies: [],
            powerups: [],
            lastSpawnTime: 0,
            lastPowerupTime: 0,
            powerupActive: [false, false, false],
            powerupTypes: ['double', 'rapid', 'shield']
        };

        // 获取DOM元素
        const canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');
        const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
        const scoreElement = document.getElementById('score');
        const livesElement = document.getElementById('lives');
        const levelElement = document.getElementById('level');
        const finalScoreElement = document.getElementById('finalScore');
        const startScreen = document.getElementById('startScreen');
        const gameOverScreen = document.getElementById('gameOver');
        const startBtn = document.getElementById('startBtn');
        const restartBtn = document.getElementById('restartBtn');
        const leftBtn = document.getElementById('leftBtn');
        const rightBtn = document.getElementById('rightBtn');
        const fireBtn = document.getElementById('fireBtn');
        const powerupElements = [
            document.getElementById('powerup1'),
            document.getElementById('powerup2'),
            document.getElementById('powerup3')
        ];

        // 设置画布尺寸
        function resizeCanvas() {
            const container = document.querySelector('.game-container');
            canvas.width = container.clientWidth;
            canvas.height = container.clientHeight;

            // 更新游戏常量
            CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH = canvas.width;
            CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT = canvas.height;
            gameState.playerX = CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH / 2;
            gameState.playerY = CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT - 100;
        }

        // 初始化游戏
        function initGame() {
            resizeCanvas();

            // 事件监听
            window.addEventListener('resize', resizeCanvas);

            // 键盘控制
            window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
                gameState.keys[e.key] = true;
            });

            window.addEventListener('keyup', (e) => {
                gameState.keys[e.key] = false;
            });

            // 触摸控制
            canvas.addEventListener('touchstart', (e) => {
                const touch = e.touches[0];
                gameState.touchStartX = touch.clientX;
            });

            canvas.addEventListener('touchmove', (e) => {
                if (!gameState.gameStarted || gameState.gameOver) return;

                const touch = e.touches[0];
                const deltaX = touch.clientX - gameState.touchStartX;

                if (Math.abs(deltaX) > 10) {
                    if (deltaX > 0) {
                        gameState.playerX = Math.min(CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, gameState.playerX + CONFIG.PLAYER_SPEED * 2);
                    } else {
                        gameState.playerX = Math.max(CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SPEED * 2);
                    }
                    gameState.touchStartX = touch.clientX;
                }
            });

            // 按钮事件
            leftBtn.addEventListener('touchstart', () => gameState.keys['ArrowLeft'] = true);
            leftBtn.addEventListener('touchend', () => gameState.keys['ArrowLeft'] = false);

            rightBtn.addEventListener('touchstart', () => gameState.keys['ArrowRight'] = true);
            rightBtn.addEventListener('touchend', () => gameState.keys['ArrowRight'] = false);

            fireBtn.addEventListener('touchstart', fireBullet);

            // 开始/重新开始按钮
            startBtn.addEventListener('click', startGame);
            restartBtn.addEventListener('click', startGame);

            // 创建背景粒子
            createParticles();

            // 开始游戏循环
            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);
        }

        // 创建背景粒子
        function createParticles() {
            const particlesContainer = document.getElementById('particles');
            particlesContainer.innerHTML = '';

            const particleCount = 100;
            for (let i = 0; i < particleCount; i++) {
                const particle = document.createElement('div');
                particle.style.position = 'absolute';
                particle.style.width = Math.random() * 3 + 1 + 'px';
                particle.style.height = particle.style.width;
                particle.style.backgroundColor = `hsl(${Math.random() * 60 + 200}, 70%, 60%)`;
                particle.style.borderRadius = '50%';
                particle.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
                particle.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%';
                particle.style.opacity = Math.random() * 0.5 + 0.1;
                particle.style.animation = `float ${Math.random() * 20 + 10}s infinite linear`;
                particlesContainer.appendChild(particle);
            }
        }

        // 开始游戏
        function startGame() {
            // 重置游戏状态
            gameState.score = 0;
            gameState.lives = 3;
            gameState.level = 1;
            gameState.gameOver = false;
            gameState.gameStarted = true;
            gameState.bullets = [];
            gameState.enemies = [];
            gameState.powerups = [];
            gameState.powerupActive = [false, false, false];

            // 更新UI
            updateUI();

            // 隐藏开始屏幕和游戏结束屏幕
            startScreen.classList.add('hidden');
            gameOverScreen.classList.remove('active');
        }

        // 更新UI
        function updateUI() {
            scoreElement.textContent = gameState.score;
            livesElement.textContent = gameState.lives;
            levelElement.textContent = gameState.level;
            finalScoreElement.textContent = gameState.score;

            // 更新能量道具UI
            for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
                if (gameState.powerupActive[i]) {
                    powerupElements[i].style.backgroundColor = 'rgba(0, 150, 255, 0.7)';
                    powerupElements[i].style.color = 'white';
                } else {
                    powerupElements[i].style.backgroundColor = 'rgba(0, 30, 60, 0.7)';
                    powerupElements[i].style.color = '#64c8ff';
                }
            }
        }

        // 创建玩家子弹
        function fireBullet() {
            if (!gameState.gameStarted || gameState.gameOver) return;

            // 根据当前激活的能量道具决定射击模式
            if (gameState.powerupActive[0]) { // 双发
                gameState.bullets.push({
                    x: gameState.playerX - 15,
                    y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE,
                    width: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE,
                    height: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE * 2,
                    speed: CONFIG.BULLET_SPEED,
                    color: '#00ccff'
                });
                gameState.bullets.push({
                    x: gameState.playerX + 15,
                    y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE,
                    width: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE,
                    height: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE * 2,
                    speed: CONFIG.BULLET_SPEED,
                    color: '#00ccff'
                });
            } else if (gameState.powerupActive[1]) { // 连发
                for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        gameState.bullets.push({
                            x: gameState.playerX + (Math.random() * 20 - 10),
                            y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE,
                            width: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE,
                            height: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE * 2,
                            speed: CONFIG.BULLET_SPEED + 2,
                            color: '#ffcc00'
                        });
                    }, i * 100);
                }
            } else { // 普通射击
                gameState.bullets.push({
                    x: gameState.playerX,
                    y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE,
                    width: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE,
                    height: CONFIG.BULLET_SIZE * 2,
                    speed: CONFIG.BULLET_SPEED,
                    color: '#00ffcc'
                });
            }
        }

        // 生成敌人
        function spawnEnemy() {
            if (gameState.enemies.length >= CONFIG.MAX_ENEMIES + gameState.level - 1) return;

            const size = CONFIG.ENEMY_SIZE + Math.random() * 10;
            const type = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3); // 0: 普通, 1: 快速, 2: 大型

            gameState.enemies.push({
                x: Math.random() * (CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH - size * 2) + size,
                y: -size,
                width: size,
                height: size,
                speed: CONFIG.ENEMY_SPEED + (gameState.level - 1) * CONFIG.LEVEL_SPEED_INCREASE,
                type: type,
                color: type === 0 ? '#ff6464' : type === 1 ? '#ffcc00' : '#ff00cc',
                health: type === 2 ? 3 : 1
            });
        }

        // 生成能量道具
        function spawnPowerup() {
            if (gameState.powerups.length >= CONFIG.MAX_POWERUPS) return;

            const type = Math.floor(Math.random() * 3);
            const size = CONFIG.POWERUP_SIZE;

            gameState.powerups.push({
                x: Math.random() * (CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH - size * 2) + size,
                y: -size,
                width: size,
                height: size,
                speed: CONFIG.POWERUP_SPEED,
                type: type,
                color: type === 0 ? '#00ccff' : type === 1 ? '#ffcc00' : '#00ff99'
            });
        }

        // 更新游戏状态
        function update() {
            if (!gameState.gameStarted || gameState.gameOver) return;

            // 玩家移动
            if (gameState.keys['ArrowLeft'] || gameState.keys['a']) {
                gameState.playerX = Math.max(CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SPEED);
            }
            if (gameState.keys['ArrowRight'] || gameState.keys['d']) {
                gameState.playerX = Math.min(CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, gameState.playerX + CONFIG.PLAYER_SPEED);
            }

            // 自动射击
            if (gameState.keys[' '] || gameState.keys['Enter']) {
                fireBullet();
            }

            // 生成敌人
            if (Math.random() * CONFIG.SPAWN_RATE < 1) {
                spawnEnemy();
            }

            // 生成能量道具
            if (Math.random() * CONFIG.POWERUP_SPAWN_RATE < 1) {
                spawnPowerup();
            }

            // 更新子弹
            for (let i = gameState.bullets.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
                const bullet = gameState.bullets[i];
                bullet.y -= bullet.speed;

                // 移除超出屏幕的子弹
                if (bullet.y + bullet.height < 0) {
                    gameState.bullets.splice(i, 1);
                    continue;
                }

                // 检测子弹与敌人的碰撞
                for (let j = gameState.enemies.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                    const enemy = gameState.enemies[j];
                    if (checkCollision(bullet, enemy)) {
                        // 减少敌人生命值
                        enemy.health--;

                        // 如果敌人生命值为0，移除敌人并增加分数
                        if (enemy.health <= 0) {
                            gameState.enemies.splice(j, 1);
                            gameState.score += enemy.type === 2 ? 50 : 20;

                            // 检查是否升级
                            if (gameState.score >= CONFIG.LEVEL_UP_THRESHOLD * gameState.level) {
                                gameState.level++;
                            }
                        }

                        // 移除子弹
                        gameState.bullets.splice(i, 1);
                        break;
                    }
                }
            }

            // 更新敌人
            for (let i = gameState.enemies.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
                const enemy = gameState.enemies[i];
                enemy.y += enemy.speed;

                // 检测敌人是否到达底部
                if (enemy.y > CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT) {
                    gameState.enemies.splice(i, 1);
                    gameState.lives--;

                    // 检查游戏是否结束
                    if (gameState.lives <= 0) {
                        endGame();
                    }
                    continue;
                }

                // 检测敌人与玩家的碰撞
                if (checkCollision(
                    {x: gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, width: CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, height: CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE},
                    enemy
                )) {
                    gameState.enemies.splice(i, 1);
                    gameState.lives--;

                    // 检查游戏是否结束
                    if (gameState.lives <= 0) {
                        endGame();
                    }
                }
            }

            // 更新能量道具
            for (let i = gameState.powerups.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
                const powerup = gameState.powerups[i];
                powerup.y += powerup.speed;

                // 移除超出屏幕的能量道具
                if (powerup.y > CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT) {
                    gameState.powerups.splice(i, 1);
                    continue;
                }

                // 检测能量道具与玩家的碰撞
                if (checkCollision(
                    {x: gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, y: gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, width: CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, height: CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE},
                    powerup
                )) {
                    // 激活能量道具
                    if (!gameState.powerupActive[powerup.type]) {
                        gameState.powerupActive[powerup.type] = true;

                        // 设置能量道具过期时间（10秒）
                        setTimeout(() => {
                            gameState.powerupActive[powerup.type] = false;
                            updateUI();
                        }, 10000);

                        updateUI();
                    }

                    gameState.powerups.splice(i, 1);
                }
            }

            // 更新UI
            updateUI();
        }

        // 检测碰撞
        function checkCollision(obj1, obj2) {
            return obj1.x < obj2.x + obj2.width &&
                   obj1.x + obj1.width > obj2.x &&
                   obj1.y < obj2.y + obj2.height &&
                   obj1.y + obj1.height > obj2.y;
        }

        // 结束游戏
        function endGame() {
            gameState.gameOver = true;
            gameOverScreen.classList.add('active');
        }

        // 绘制游戏
        function draw() {
            // 清空画布
            ctx.clearRect(0, 0, CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH, CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT);

            // 绘制星空背景
            drawStars();

            // 绘制玩家
            drawPlayer();

            // 绘制子弹
            drawBullets();

            // 绘制敌人
            drawEnemies();

            // 绘制能量道具
            drawPowerups();

            // 绘制能量道具激活效果
            drawPowerupEffects();
        }

        // 绘制星空背景
        function drawStars() {
            ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(10, 15, 35, 0.7)';
            ctx.fillRect(0, 0, CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH, CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT);

            // 绘制星星
            ctx.fillStyle = 'white';
            for (let i = 0; i < 200; i++) {
                const x = (i * 13) % CONFIG.CANVAS_WIDTH;
                const y = (i * 17) % CONFIG.CANVAS_HEIGHT;
                const size = Math.sin(i * 0.1) * 1.5 + 0.5;
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(x, y, size, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();
            }
        }

        // 绘制玩家
        function drawPlayer() {
            // 绘制飞船主体
            ctx.fillStyle = '#64c8ff';
            ctx.beginPath();
            ctx.moveTo(gameState.playerX, gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2);
            ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2);
            ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2);
            ctx.closePath();
            ctx.fill();

            // 绘制飞船细节
            ctx.fillStyle = '#0066cc';
            ctx.beginPath();
            ctx.moveTo(gameState.playerX, gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/3);
            ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/3, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/3);
            ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/3, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/3);
            ctx.closePath();
            ctx.fill();

            // 绘制引擎火焰
            if (Math.random() > 0.7) {
                ctx.fillStyle = '#ff6400';
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.moveTo(gameState.playerX - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/4, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2);
                ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2 + 15);
                ctx.lineTo(gameState.playerX + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/4, gameState.playerY + CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2);
                ctx.closePath();
                ctx.fill();
            }
        }

        // 绘制子弹
        function drawBullets() {
            gameState.bullets.forEach(bullet => {
                ctx.fillStyle = bullet.color;
                ctx.fillRect(bullet.x - bullet.width/2, bullet.y, bullet.width, bullet.height);

                // 添加光晕效果
                ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)';
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(bullet.x, bullet.y + bullet.height/2, bullet.width, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();
            });
        }

        // 绘制敌人
        function drawEnemies() {
            gameState.enemies.forEach(enemy => {
                // 绘制敌人主体
                ctx.fillStyle = enemy.color;
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(enemy.x, enemy.y, enemy.width/2, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();

                // 绘制敌人细节
                ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)';
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(enemy.x - enemy.width/4, enemy.y - enemy.width/4, enemy.width/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.arc(enemy.x + enemy.width/4, enemy.y - enemy.width/4, enemy.width/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.arc(enemy.x, enemy.y + enemy.width/4, enemy.width/4, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();

                // 绘制敌人生命值条
                if (enemy.health > 1) {
                    ctx.fillStyle = '#ff0000';
                    ctx.fillRect(enemy.x - enemy.width/2, enemy.y - enemy.width/2 - 10, enemy.width, 5);
                    ctx.fillStyle = '#00ff00';
                    ctx.fillRect(enemy.x - enemy.width/2, enemy.y - enemy.width/2 - 10, enemy.width * (enemy.health / 3), 5);
                }
            });
        }

        // 绘制能量道具
        function drawPowerups() {
            gameState.powerups.forEach(powerup => {
                // 绘制道具主体
                ctx.fillStyle = powerup.color;
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(powerup.x, powerup.y, powerup.width/2, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();

                // 绘制道具图标
                ctx.fillStyle = 'white';
                ctx.font = 'bold 20px Arial';
                ctx.textAlign = 'center';
                ctx.textBaseline = 'middle';
                ctx.fillText(
                    powerup.type === 0 ? '✚' : powerup.type === 1 ? '❄' : '✪',
                    powerup.x, powerup.y
                );
            });
        }

        // 绘制能量道具激活效果
        function drawPowerupEffects() {
            if (gameState.powerupActive[0]) { // 双发效果
                ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.5)';
                ctx.lineWidth = 2;
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(gameState.playerX, gameState.playerY - CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE/2, CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.stroke();
            }

            if (gameState.powerupActive[2]) { // 护盾效果
                ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0, 255, 150, 0.7)';
                ctx.lineWidth = 3;
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(gameState.playerX, gameState.playerY, CONFIG.PLAYER_SIZE * 0.8, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.stroke();
            }
        }

        // 游戏主循环
        function gameLoop() {
            update();
            draw();
            requestAnimationFrame(gameLoop);
        }

        // 初始化游戏
        window.onload = initGame;
    </script>

    <style>
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: translateY(-100vh) rotate(360deg); }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
```

## 游戏特点

1. **手机端优化**：
   - 完全适配手机屏幕，支持触摸操作
   - 虚拟控制按钮（左右移动和射击）
   - 响应式设计，适应不同屏幕尺寸

2. **游戏内容**：
   - 三种不同类型的敌人（普通、快速、大型）
   - 三种能量道具（双发、连发、护盾）
   - 多关卡系统，难度随关卡提升
   - 分数系统和生命值管理

3. **视觉效果**：
   - 动态星空背景
   - 粒子效果
   - 精美的飞船和敌人设计
   - 能量道具激活特效

4. **游戏机制**：
   - 碰撞检测系统
   - 敌人生命值系统（大型敌人需要多次击中）
   - 能量道具10秒持续时间
   - 关卡升级机制（分数达到阈值升级）

## 操作方法

- **移动飞船**：点击左右箭头按钮或左右滑动屏幕
- **发射子弹**：点击中间的圆形按钮
- **开始游戏**：点击"开始游戏"按钮
- **重新开始**：游戏结束后点击"重新开始"按钮

游戏难度适中但具有挑战性，随着关卡提升敌人数量和速度会增加，需要玩家灵活运用能量道具来应对越来越强的敌人。

